{"title":"少女·太阳","authors":["江义勇"],"dates":[{"year":1990,"month":11,"day":30}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"少女·太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江义勇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨风轻轻儿吹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"野花淡淡儿香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小路旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一位红衣姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晨读的琅琅书声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引起我好奇的联想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在给孩子们上课"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲祖国的明天，祖国的期望；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在为外宾导游"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说长城的伟大，故宫的辉煌；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她在与朋友谈心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诉少女的秘密，青春的向往……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦，好姑娘"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你像一团燃烧的火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春的光热"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来自每天每天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冉冉升起的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火红的太阳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"给母校"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毕业留言"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果在边远的乡村"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一柱红烛的光明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是您的火种"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点燃它透明的烛芯；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果在璀璨的星空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一颗闪光的星星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是您的汗珠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凝成它闪光的生命；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"如果在汹涌的海上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有一名无畏的水手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是您的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铸就它不屈的灵魂！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（作者单位：中央党校）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}